title: Live From The Nashville Comedy Festival Show 2  Crack Smoke In Yo Body! | Ep. 180

description:
SEE THE COLDEST PODCAST LIVE IN YOUR CITY! https://www.85southshow.com/live The coldest young comedians in the game turn up for the second sold out 85 South Show at the nashville comedy festival. The first show was hilarious but in the second, DC Karlous and Chico Bean hit their stride and bring the non-stop laughs. You know they roasted everybody in the audience and take it down memory lane - reminiscing about growing up with off brand clothes and food! In this episode the fellas create an all-new catchy hit " Crack Smoke in Yo Body!" #85southshow #dcyoungfly #karlousmiller #chicobean FOLLOW THE CREW KARLOUS MILLER - https://www.facebook.com/karlousm/ DCYOUNGFLY - https://www.facebook.com/DcYoungFly1/ CHICO BEAN - https://www.facebook.com/OldSchoolFool/ BILLY SORRELLS - https://www.facebook.com/billysorrells/ FAT AND PAID - https://www.facebook.com/Fatandpaid/ DARREN BRAND - https://www.facebook.com/darrenbigbab... CLAYTON ENGLISH - http://www.claytonenglish.com/ JOE T.
